description: Details of protection of interior elements pursuant to condition 7 of Listed Building Consent ref: P/2007/3166 dated 08/02/2008 for Internal and external alterations to Norwood Hall and attached conservatory, including the removal of two existing external staircases and erection of one replacement external staircase, installation of wheelchair platform/stairlift access to north elevation entrance, works to walled garden including landscaping, removal of greenhouses and works to walls, works within grounds including the removal of outbuildings, greenhouses and structures in conjunction with the formation of parking areas, pedestrian and vehicular routes and accesses, the erection of a part single, two and three-storey two-form entry Primary and Nursery School on the west  part of the site, and use of Norwood Hall as an Adult Education and Community Centre
